        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Have a project in mind? We'd love to hear about it. Send us a message and let's discuss how we can help bring your vision to life.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/25 transition-all">
            Start Your Project
